{"tid":725232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本來我係唔信窮撚生仔其實真係好自私","createTime":"2018-07-01T14:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:51:08.000Z","uid":162268,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6ca5a8073e8f68bac99228a926cf2574ba5a37","tid":725232,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"話說今日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五十幾歲同事    <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：點呀細路，返pt 洗唔洗俾家用老母呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：仲俾家用？佢哋都冇俾學費我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗交學費                    咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你呀媽養大你唔洗錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我立即問佢一句，你生仔為咩？為咗養你咩，我就唔覺得養父母係必要。<br />\n<br />\n佢由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：生仔就係為咗養自己啦。再者，咁辛苦養大佢，佢第時一定要養返我。你個不孝子老母生你出嚟真係......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：自己都未養好自己仲俾錢老豆老母，俾哂啲錢老豆老母，之後再申請老綜咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就唔撚出聲，同第二個同事圍內取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上真係真人真事，喺我出post一個鐘前發生"},{"pid":"0876ad69bef91485afcae4e188d137b4f288ea73","tid":725232,"uid":150270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\"